<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you set the $user parameter to an empty() value in the constructor for a subclass of Zend_Service_Rackspace_Abstract you get stuck in an endless loop, as it repeatedly calls authenticate().</p>

<p>Steps to reproduce:</p>

<p>$cf = new Zend_Service_Rackspace_Files(null, null);
$containers = $cf-&gt;getContainers();</p>

<p>Expected result:</p>

<p>A catchable exception</p>

<p>Actual result:</p>

<p>Fatal error: Maximum function nesting level of '100' reached, aborting! in /Users/matt/www/httpd/1_8_3/library/Zend/Service/Rackspace/Abstract.php on line 260</p>

